description: Demolition of commercial and residential properties, site clearance and redevelopment comprising - The construction of a mixed-use development comprising five blocks with 527 residential units (311 private units, 108 shared ownership units and 108 affordable rent units), a multiscreen cinema (Use Class D2) of 5,267sqm (GEA), 9,830sqm (GEA) of retail, restaurant and cafe uses (Use Classes A1, A2, A3, A4 and A5), infrastructure including 513 parking spaces, 686 cycle parking spaces, service areas, public realm incorporating pedestrian/cycle circulation areas with associated hard and soft landscaping and private amenity spaces (Amended drawings)
